                     <interp inst="t18470816-1750-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> stealing 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18470816-name-245" type="victimName">
